{"tid":2362650,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"36歲尹恩惠屢傳整容 笑到變小丑被質疑再動刀","createTime":"2021-01-11T14:56:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T23:40:39.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bfd0b19298fd45c7c5e6be063feba775203d1616","tid":2362650,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T14:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LIxM7tNeOLLeavZYw9_fb0pTMgk=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JMN46IVS3JHZPM5CPRHTKEFYXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLIxM7tNeOLLeavZYw9_fb0pTMgk%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJMN46IVS3JHZPM5CPRHTKEFYXA.jpg&h=c59e7701&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現年36歲的韓國女星尹恩惠，近期頻頻更新IG及個人YouTube頻道Keep住曝光，在日前的影片中，她就素顏出鏡分享減肥餐單。<br />\n<br />\n皺紋盡現<br />\n尹恩惠今日再度在IG公開新相，並留言寫道：「祝你度過愉快的一天。」而她在相中的穿着打扮跟影片一樣，估計是攝於同一日。相中，尹恩惠先是木無表情望着鏡頭，加上其衣着、髮型，顯得清純。但在另一相中，她對着鏡頭露出笑容時皺紋盡現，其嘴角紋與蘋果肌更似乎連成一線，導致其臉部如經典電影角色小丑（Joker）般，顯得十分奇怪，令屢傳整容的她被質疑是否再動刀。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Vi1RCDmancW6U-hLkW_ptD74erA=/802x802/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2VQI2IKCLFFSRA7WN3WCANZQCQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVi1RCDmancW6U-hLkW_ptD74erA%3D%2F802x802%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2VQI2IKCLFFSRA7WN3WCANZQCQ.jpg&h=9783f028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wf3LIBODc0OppTvcsF9sEMRA__k=/802x839/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6RUJMZYLIZEAFG5FJOF5UPJS5A.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fwf3LIBODc0OppTvcsF9sEMRA__k%3D%2F802x839%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fclo